# Vehicle Service Mapping System Enhancement Proposal

## 1. Enhanced User Registration System

### User Type Selection
The system will be enhanced to include two types of user accounts:

**Regular Users:**
- Can search for services
- Save favorite stations
- Use route planning features
- Manage vehicle profiles

**Service Owners:**
- Can register their businesses
- Add multiple service locations
- Upload photos and service details
- Update business information
- Manage service listings

### Implementation Details:
- Add user type selection during registration
- Create separate registration flows for each user type
- Implement role-based access control
- Business verification process for service owners

## 2. Vehicle Profile Management System

### Vehicle Information Tracking:
- **Vehicle Type:** Car, Motorcycle, SUV, Truck, Electric Vehicle
- **Fuel Type:** Gasoline, Diesel, Premium Gasoline, Electric
- **Tank Capacity:** Customizable based on vehicle type
- **Current Fuel Level:** Real-time tracking with percentage input
- **Fuel Consumption Rate:** Calculate based on vehicle type and driving habits

### Features:
- Multiple vehicle profiles per user
- Fuel level monitoring with visual indicators
- Range calculation based on current fuel level
- Service recommendations based on vehicle type

## 3. Expanded Service Categories

### New Service Types:

**1. Vulcanizing Shops**
- Tire repair services
- Wheel alignment
- Tire replacement
- Emergency tire services

**2. Repair Shops**
- Mechanical repairs
- Electrical system services
- Engine diagnostics
- Preventive maintenance

**3. Car Wash Services**
- Automatic car wash
- Manual cleaning
- Detailing services
- Interior cleaning

**4. Auto Parts Stores**
- Genuine parts
- Aftermarket parts
- Accessories
- Installation services

### Service Details:
- Operating hours
- Contact information
- Service specialties
- Price ranges
- Customer ratings

## 4. Visual Documentation System

### Photo Gallery Features:
- **Service Location Photos:** Actual images of service establishments
- **Service Area Photos:** Pictures of working areas and equipment
- **Facility Photos:** Customer area, payment counters, waiting areas
- **User-Uploaded Photos:** Customer-submitted service photos
- **Verification Photos:** Official business documentation

### Implementation:
- Image upload functionality for service owners
- Photo moderation system
- Multiple image support per service location
- Mobile-optimized image viewing

## 5. Personalization and Favorites System

### Favorite Stations Feature:
- **Save Preferred Stations:** Users can bookmark frequently visited services
- **Quick Access:** One-tap access to favorite locations
- **Personal Notes:** Add custom notes to saved locations
- **Rating System:** Rate and review services
- **Visit History:** Track previously visited service locations

### Filtering Options:
- Filter by service type
- Filter by distance
- Filter by ratings
- Filter by price range
- Filter by operating hours

## 6. Geographic Expansion and Accuracy

### Area Expansion:
- **Wider Coverage:** Expand beyond current geographic limits
- **Rural Area Inclusion:** Add services in suburban and rural areas
- **International Scaling:** Prepare for multi-region support

### GPS Accuracy Improvements:
- **Enhanced Location Services:** Improved GPS coordinate collection
- **Address Verification:** Validate service location addresses
- **Map Precision:** Higher resolution mapping data
- **Real-time Updates:** Dynamic location accuracy improvements

## 7. Smart Fuel Management System

### Fuel Level Monitoring:
- **Manual Input:** Users enter current fuel level percentage
- **Tank Capacity Settings:** Customizable based on vehicle
- **Range Calculation:** Automatic distance-to-empty calculation
- **Low Fuel Alerts:** Notifications when fuel is critically low

### Intelligent Recommendations:
- **Route Planning:** Suggest routes with service stations along the way
- **Emergency Services:** Highlight nearby services when fuel is low
- **Price Comparisons:** Show fuel prices at nearby stations
- **Service Availability:** Real-time service status updates

## Technical Implementation Requirements

### Database Enhancements:
- New tables for vehicle profiles
- Expanded service categories table
- User preferences and favorites table
- Photo storage and management system

### Frontend Updates:
- Enhanced user interface for new features
- Mobile-responsive design improvements
- Real-time data updates
- Interactive map enhancements

### Backend Services:
- Advanced search algorithms
- Route optimization with fuel considerations
- Image processing and storage
- Notification services

This enhanced system will provide comprehensive vehicle service management, personalized user experiences, and intelligent service recommendations based on real-time vehicle needs and user preferences.
